{"title":"劳动发家快生产","authors":["马如龙"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":5,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动发家快生产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马如龙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫老乡，听我拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要说说怕发家："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕斗争，怕发家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他怕村上数着他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壶关有个赵老汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"查田运动他害怕；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他光怕给他割尾巴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动起家不斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天吃个光踏踏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卖晌赚了麦一石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里长着核桃树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍下当柴烧了他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大驴怀上小驴驹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他愁眉不展心事大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他想道两驴就要割一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再下一个就割俩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从去冬到现在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都没斗争他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家说你是劳动发的家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大胆致富莫害怕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年春耕动员会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说“我可后悔啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是听上大家话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事情永远办不差”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老乡们，发家吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事情永远办不差”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕三余一要做到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动发家永不怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户都富了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋贼不愁打不垮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家都要订计划。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋后要开群英会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看一看谁的本事大。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}